nsion]], [[diabetes]], [[paraplegia]] etc., and is also a heart patient with a [[Artificial cardiac pacemaker|pacemaker]]. She was discharged from hospital on 19 February.<ref name=\"two cured COVID-19\">{{cite web|url=https://www.vir.com.vn/two-more-covid-19-patients-in-malaysia-discharged-74053.html|title=Two more COVID-19 patients in Malaysia discharged|work=CNA|via=Vietnam Investment Review|date=20 February 2020|accessdate=26 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226052650/https://www.vir.com.vn/two-more-covid-19-patients-in-malaysia-discharged-74053.html|archive-date=26 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Discharged\n|-\n| 18\n|\n| 9 February 2020\n| 19 February 2020\n| 31\n| {{MYS}}\n| A Malaysian male national from [[Kuala Langat District]] of Selangor. He worked in [[Macau]] and had been to mainland China on 1 February where he later developed cough symptoms on 7 February. He was admitted to a hospital in Malaysia on the same day and was diagnosed with the virus on 9 February.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2020/02/10/18th-person-diagnosed-with-novel-coronavirus-in-m039sia|title=18th person diagnosed with novel coronavirus in M'sia|work=The Star|date=10 February 2020|accessdate=23 February 2020}}</ref> After achieving a full recovery, he was discharged from the hospital on 19 February.<ref name=\"two cured COVID-19\"/>\n| Discharged\n|-\n| 19\n| G5\n| 13 February 2020\n| 24 February 2020\n| 39\n| {{CHN}}\n| A Chinese female national from Wuhan. Arrived in Malaysia with four relatives and friends on 25 January. She had fever and cough on 12 February and was diagnosed with the virus on 13 February.<ref name=\"three infected Chinese national\"/> After successfully being cured through treatment, she was discharged from hospital on 24 February.<ref name=\"two Chinese nationals COVID-19 patient discharged\"/>\n| Discharged\n|-\n| 20\n|\n| 14 February 2020\n| 19 February 2020\n| 27\n| {{CHN}}\n| A Chinese male na